This app definitely works for my 2012 nissan versa hatchback with the mr18de manual transmission.  My only complaint is that to unlock anything you have to make in app purchases.  Most reviews that complain about it not working are likely because the Bluetooth adapter being used is not able to issue commands.  The other reason it may not work is because in modern vehicles the CAN Bus can have a primitive for of security making commands unavailable through the standard obd2 port.  I recommend this app.
